The paper discusses the architecture and processes involved in a Question Answering System, which falls under the sub-category of Natural Language Processing (NLP) and Computational Linguistics (cs.CL). The paper also mentions the use of machine learning techniques such as Support Vector Machines (SVM) and Decision Trees, which are commonly used in Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI). Information Retrieval (cs.IR) is also relevant as the paper discusses the process of retrieving relevant web pages and providing the most relevant answer. The paper also suggests further areas of research, which could fall under the sub-categories of Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Cybernetics (cs.CY).
